# >>> repo-harness:gitignore-private-boundary >>>
# Maintainer notes — not part of the project; they live in the private notes repo,
# reachable through the `local` symlink. NO trailing slash on any path in this block:
# a worktree materializes these paths as SYMLINKS, and a `foo/` pattern matches a real
# directory only — the ignore then keeps working in the main tree and silently fails
# in every worktree.
/local

